title.narrative: 5.3 SYSTEM STRENGTHENING & POLICYSUPPORT

description.narrative: 5.3 Increased capacity to legislate, plan and budget to improve Water, Sanitation, and Hygiene (WASH) systems, including mainstreaming disaster risk management, which contributes to Children In Urban Settings / Local Governance, Disaster Risk Reduction, Environmental Sustainability, Sanitation, Sanitation (Covid), Water. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2022, children and their families have improved and equitable access to and use of safe and sustainable drinking water and sanitation services, and improved hygiene practices.
